    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it as much as I have. Come check it out, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
