      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered legend, maintained to an exacting standard. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a perfectly synchronized VANOS system and crisp individual throttle body response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and an uncompromised subframe. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep luster with zero oxidative degradation or panel misalignment. This is a collector-grade specimen with a documented service history, ready for the most discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
