    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish completely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats still possess their factory-fresh aroma and supple texture, with absolutely no signs of wear or bolster compression. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule documented by a comprehensive folder of original service records. The undercarriage is equally impressive, devoid of any road debris or corrosion. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly immaculate example of automotive excellence that has been pampered since day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
